            <title>[HBASE-2415] Disable META splitting in 0.20</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2415</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We know that META splitting doesn&apos;t work correctly in 0.20, eg &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1852&quot; title=&quot;HConnectionManager.testTableOnlineState will get into infinite loop if more than one .META. region&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-1852&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-1852&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and others. Granted, META will only split for very big tables, but we should just explicitly disable splitting of this region.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12461337">HBASE-2415</key>
            <summary>Disable META splitting in 0.20</summary>
