                            <comment id="12854306" author="tlipcon" created="Wed, 7 Apr 2010 02:51:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Pretty trivial patch. I think this is the right way to go about it? It seems to have worked in my testing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12854361" author="streamy" created="Wed, 7 Apr 2010 06:29:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch looks good but this code changes in my patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2375&quot; title=&quot;Revisit compaction configuration parameters&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-2375&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-2375&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.  Will keep open so it doesn&apos;t get squashed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12854601" author="stack" created="Wed, 7 Apr 2010 17:09:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Jon: I want to commit this.  Are you suggesting no?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12854633" author="tlipcon" created="Wed, 7 Apr 2010 18:13:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;IMO we may as well commit it, I&apos;ll make a note to double check &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2375&quot; title=&quot;Revisit compaction configuration parameters&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-2375&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-2375&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&apos;s patch to make sure it&apos;s maintained. But it sounds like that patch is a bigger change so not a candidate for this upcoming release, whereas we might as well get this simple fix in.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12854670" author="streamy" created="Wed, 7 Apr 2010 20:02:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Issues are linked so I won&apos;t forget.  Just commit.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We could add a unit test to make sure we prevent a regression?  I&apos;m okay w/o just an idea, the change is simple.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
